~~=~~
0.8261
.EN
.EQ
CCTF sub WDA lineup =~~ cctf
~~=~~
1 - 0.18(0.2) over {  ( 0.15 + 0.18 ) }
~~=~~
0.8909
.EN
The calculation for the CCTF will be covered in detail so do not fret that you
have not been given an explanation at this stage.
